---
title: Sausage & Tomato Soup Bar One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: Introducing our chef-curated “perfect bowls,” where everyone at the table can customize their own! This lineup stars a hearty pork sausage-packed tomato soup with a variety of tantalizing toppers—mozzarella, wilted spinach, croutons, and sour cream. Serve it all up with a crisp green salad on the side.
